</span></span></code></pre></div></div></div></div><p>The arguments for the <code>--no-cache-filter</code> flag must be names of stages.</p><h3 class="scroll-mt-20" id="output"><a class="text-black dark:text-white no-underline hover:underline" href="https://docs.docker.com/reference/cli/docker/buildx/build/#output">Set the export action for the build result (-o, --output)</a></h3><div data-pagefind-ignore="" class="scroll-mt-20" x-data="" x-ref="root"><div class="group relative"><button x-data="{ code: 'LW8sIC0tb3V0cHV0PVtQQVRILC0sdHlwZT1UWVBFWyxLRVk9VkFMVUVd', copying: false }" class="absolute right-3 top-3 z-10 text-gray-light-300 dark:text-gray-dark-600" title="copy" @click="window.navigator.clipboard.writeText(atob(code).replaceAll(/^[\$>]\s+/gm, ''));
